# =============================================================================
# live2d-fork .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Excludes heavy/proprietary model assets. Source code, configs, and scripts
# are committed. To use the widget, the user must supply their own Live2D
# model files at vampire/vampire_vts/<your-model>/.
#
# 2026-06-12 policy change: A1 (full static mirror for Cloudflare Pages)
# The vampire/vampire_vts/ tree is now tracked in git so Cloudflare Pages
# can serve the model from BAZOOKA-free static infrastructure. This matches
# the upstream YuriCrystal/ai-avatar-bot repo's posture (model3.json +
# .exp3.json + .2048 textures + motion3.json + small JSON metadata).
#
# Binary .moc3 / .cdi3 / .physics3.json / .vtube.json remain ignored: the
# runtime loads them via .model3.json reference indirection, and the
# .2048 textures + exp3 metadata are sufficient for the widget to render
# the model fully (Cubism 5.x self-contained render path).
#
# Consumers running their own model should:
#   1. Replace `vampire/vampire_vts/` with their own assets
#   2. Update `vampire.txt` (license/attribution)
#   3. Re-run `scripts/Verify_Vampire_Model.py` to sanity-check params

# --- Binary Live2D model internals (still ignored) ---
*.moc3
*.moc
*.cdi3
*.physics3.json
*.vtube.json
*.zip

# --- Local-only copies of model on different paths (not canonical) ---
backend/static/live2d/
frontend/live2d/    # mirror copies of model — not for redistribution
frontend/live2d/**/*.moc3
frontend/live2d/**/*.png
frontend/live2d/**/*.physics3.json
frontend/live2d/**/texture_*
scripts/vampire/

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/

# --- Node / front-end ---
node_modules/
.npm
.yarn
dist/
build/
*.log

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Local env / secrets ---
.env
.env.local
*.local

# --- Runtime / test artifacts ---
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.backup
scripts/result.txt
scripts/vampire_param_ids.txt
scripts/zip_*.txt

# --- CSP violation reports (runtime audit logs; never commit) ---
backend/logs/
backend/logs/*.jsonl
backend/logs/*.old

# --- FastAPI stdout/stderr logs ---
backend/stdout.log
backend/stderr.log
